	   <tr><td colspan=2>i understand that DKP represents a point system used by uber guilds to award loot, but what does it stand for and how does it work?<br>&nbsp;<br>Karhas Starlance<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=85870" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=85870</a><br>Fennin Ro<br>"He slices, he dices, he fits in your carry-on luggage!"</td></tr>
